com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.reasoner.classification

Interface SnomedReasonerService


  • public interface SnomedReasonerService
    Represents the RPC interface for the SNOMED CT reasoner service.

    Supported operations are:

    • starting classification of a branch
    • retrieving a classification result for review
    • returning equivalence sets
    • persisting changes from a classification run
    • checking reasoner availability
    • removing a classification result

    • Method Detail

      • beginClassification

        void beginClassification(ClassificationSettings settings)
        Performs a classification run for the specified branch of SNOMED CT. Current ontology content is extended with the given concept definitions; if a definition describes a concept which already exists, the incoming definition takes precedence.
        Parameters:
        settings - the object describing parameters for the classification run

      • getResult

        GetResultResponse getResult(String classificationId)
        Returns the results of the classification for review. This method blocks until a result becomes available.
        Parameters:
        classificationId - the unique identifier of the classification run
        Returns:
        a GetResultResponse instance

      • getEquivalentConcepts

        GetEquivalentConceptsResponse getEquivalentConcepts(String classificationId)
        Returns equivalent sets computed from the classification. This method blocks until a result becomes available.
        Parameters:
        classificationId - the unique identifier of the classification run
        Returns:
        a GetEquivalentConceptsResponse instance

      • persistChanges

        PersistChangesResponse persistChanges(String classificationId,
                                      String userId)
        Instructs the reasoner to persist the results of the classification with the given identifier.
        Parameters:
        classificationId - the unique identifier of the classification run
        userId - the requesting user's identifier
        Returns:
        a PersistChangesResponse instance

      • canStartImmediately

        boolean canStartImmediately()
        Checks if any free reasoner instances are available.
        Returns:
        true if a request for classification is likely to start in a short time, false otherwise

      • removeResult

        void removeResult(String classificationId)
        Removes the result of the classification with the given identifier from memory, it it exists.
        Parameters:
        classificationId - the unique identifier of the classification run
